Revision history for Perl Module Net::Dev:Tools::Syslog.


Mar 16 2004
   Net::Dev::Tools::Syslog  v 0.8.0
   Initial CPAN posting.
   Module still under development for tweaks and features.


Dec 21 2006
   Net::Dev::Tools::Syslog  v 1.0.0
   Modified the parser to give more user control over parsing.
   Added forwarding to listener.
   Accounted for syslog messages without HOSTNAME.
   Allow sender and listener to use user defined port, unix root
   user check only for ports below 1024.
   Providing example for each mode (send,listen,parse), example
   are in the doc and in the distribution.



